'''阿弗雷·韋伯'''（{{lang-en|Alfred Lambremont Webre}}，{{bd|1942年|||}}），[[美國|美國]]作家、[[律師|律師]]、[[未來學|未來學]]家和[[星際政治學|星際政治學]]家<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/scitech/report_he-believes-in-ufos-do-you_1080571|title=He believes in UFOs. Do you?|date=2007-02-17|work=DNA India|accessdate=2021-01-19|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120515211553/http://www.dnaindia.com/scitech/report_he-believes-in-ufos-do-you_1080571|archivedate=2012-05-15}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=https://www.tasnimnews.com/en/news/2019/12/07/2154621/iran-experiencing-most-challenging-adversary-in-persona-of-trump-us-analyst|title=Iran Experiencing Most Challenging Adversary in Persona of Trump: US Analyst|date=2019-12-07|work=Tasnim News Agency|accessdate=2021-01-19|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106233223/https://www.tasnimnews.com/en/news/2019/12/07/2154621/iran-experiencing-most-challenging-adversary-in-persona-of-trump-us-analyst|archivedate=2020-01-06}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Politics Of The Extra-Terrestrial|url=https://www.vice.com/en/article/gqnn5b/the-politics-of-the-extra-terrestrial|access-date=2021-10-24|date=2011-07-07|publisher=Vice|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211025192658/https://www.vice.com/en/article/gqnn5b/the-politics-of-the-extra-terrestrial|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=A 'turning point' on UFOs: Physicist Michio Kaku tells ufology conference the truth is out there|url=https://news.yahoo.com/a-turning-point-on-uf-os-physicist-michio-kaku-tells-uf-ology-conference-the-truth-is-out-there-090005631.html|access-date=2021-10-26|date=2019-09-13|publisher=Yahoo News|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211026074437/https://news.yahoo.com/a-turning-point-on-uf-os-physicist-michio-kaku-tells-uf-ology-conference-the-truth-is-out-there-090005631.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，曾作為{{le|吉隆坡戰爭罪行委員會|Kuala Lumpur War Crimes Commission|吉隆坡戰爭罪行法庭}}的七名法官之一。

== 生平 ==
出生於[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]][[彭薩科拉_(佛羅里達州)|彭薩科拉]]<ref name=":1" />。畢業於[[耶魯大學|耶魯大學]]。曾是[[傅爾布萊特計畫|傅爾布萊特計畫]]學者<ref>{{Cite web|title='Half-alien' group foresees disaster, Japan UFO landing|url=https://www.japantimes.co.jp/community/2008/04/01/issues/half-alien-group-foresees-disaster-japan-ufo-landing/|accessdate=2021-01-19|date=2008-04-01|last=Spiri|first=John|publisher=The Japan Times|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806153222/https://www.japantimes.co.jp/community/2008/04/01/issues/half-alien-group-foresees-disaster-japan-ufo-landing/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1971年至1972年間，韋伯在{{le|紐約市環保署|New York City Department of Environmental Protection}}擔任法律總顧問<ref name=":2">{{cite book|author1=阿弗雷·韋伯著|coauthors=許淑媛譯|title=多次元宇宙|date=2017年7月|publisher=一中心有限公司|location=台中|isbn=978-986-94891-1-9}}</ref>{{rp|52}}。1977年，韋伯以未來學家身分在[[國際斯坦福研究所|史丹佛研究所]]（SRI）工作<ref name=":2" />{{rp|52}}。在[[白宮|白宮]]（[[吉米·卡特|卡特]]政府時期）、[[五角大廈|五角大廈]]和史丹佛研究所進行的外星交流研究計劃當中，韋伯擔任主要研究員<ref name=":0" />。

2000年，韋伯在其著作《星際政治學：十年接觸》（''Exopolitics: Towards a Decade of Contact''，暫譯）中首度正式使用了「星際政治學」（Exopolitics）一詞<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.wired.com/2007/06/flyingsaucer-anniversary/|title=Out of This World: 60 Years of Flying Saucers|date=2007-06-24|work=Wired|accessdate=2021-01-19|language=en|quote=In 2000, Alfred Webre's book Exopolitics: Towards a Decade of Contact spawned Exopolitics, which has gained a lot of supporters who feel the existence of UFOs does not have to be scientifically proven.|archive-date=2021-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210517180353/https://www.wired.com/2007/06/flyingsaucer-anniversary/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。韋伯另一本在2005年出版的著作《星際政治學：宇宙中的政治、政府和法律》（''Exopolitics: Politics, Government and Law in the Universe''，暫譯）受到了前[[加拿大國防部|加拿大國防部]]長[[保羅·赫勒|保羅·赫勒]]的稱讚<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|title=Iranian TV attacks Canada using "lawyer" who believes Obama visited Mars|url=https://www.aptnnews.ca/national-news/iranian-tv-attacks-canada-using-lawyer-who-believes-obama-visited-mars/|access-date=2021-10-20|date=2012-10-11|last=Blackburn|first=Mark|work=APTN News|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211022163529/https://www.aptnnews.ca/national-news/iranian-tv-attacks-canada-using-lawyer-who-believes-obama-visited-mars/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在2011年，韋伯作為吉隆坡戰爭罪行法庭的七名法官之一<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/tony-blair/8890657/Activists-in-Malaysia-plan-war-crime-trial-of-George-W.-Bush-and-Tony-Blair.html|title=Activists in Malaysia plan 'war crime trial' of George W. Bush and Tony Blair|date=2011-11-15|work=The Telegraph|accessdate=2021-01-19|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111118101857/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/tony-blair/8890657/Activists-in-Malaysia-plan-war-crime-trial-of-George-W.-Bush-and-Tony-Blair.html|archivedate=2011-11-18}}</ref>，該組織（吉隆坡戰爭罪行委員會）是在前[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]首相[[馬哈地|馬哈地]]的倡導之下於2007年成立。

韋伯也曾經擔任過「教會與政府罪行國際法庭」（International Tribunal into Crimes of Church and State，ITCCS）的法律顧問<ref name=":3" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://presstv.com/detail/2012/10/10/265970/harper-govt-protects-canada-genocide|title=Harper govt. incites genocide of indigenous population: Analyst|work=Press TV|date=2012-10-10|accessdate=2021-10-21|language=en|archivedate=2012-10-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013213249/http://presstv.com/detail/2012/10/10/265970/harper-govt-protects-canada-genocide/}}</ref>，「[[卡洛·羅辛|太空合作研究所]]」（Institute for Cooperation in Space，ICIS）的國際部主任和財務主管<ref>{{Cite web|title=ICIS Board of Directors & Advisors|url=http://www.peaceinspace.com/ab_board.shtml|access-date=2021-10-26|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100610184459/http://www.peaceinspace.com/ab_board.shtml|archive-date=2010-06-10}}</ref>。

2017年3月，韋伯接受[[英國|英國]]《[[每日快報|每日快報]]》採訪時，聲稱[[梵蒂岡|梵蒂岡]]擁有[[時空旅行|時空旅行]]的技術、並在[[1960年代|1960年代]]將其提供給美國[[中央情報局|中央情報局]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Is the Vatican finally about to admit it has a hidden TIME MACHINE?|url=https://www.dailystar.co.uk/news/latest-news/vatican-finally-admit-hidden-time-16996732|accessdate=2021-01-19|date=2017-03-13|publisher=Dailystar.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223061119/https://www.dailystar.co.uk/news/latest-news/vatican-finally-admit-hidden-time-16996732|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=¿Creó el Vaticano una máquina del tiempo? Aseguran que sí y que ahora estaría en manos de EE.UU.|url=https://actualidad.rt.com/viral/233234-vaticano-tener-maquina-tiempo|accessdate=2021-01-19|date=2017-03-14|publisher=RT en Español|language=es|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506152324/https://actualidad.rt.com/viral/233234-vaticano-tener-maquina-tiempo|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

